Subject: scsi_dh: check queuedata pointer before proceeding further
Git-commit: scsi-misc a18a920c70d48a8e4a2b750d8a183b3c1a4be514
Patch-Mainline: included in scsi-misc
References: bnc#721738

This patch validates sdev pointer in scsi_dh_activate before proceeding further.

Without this check we might see the panic as below. I have seen this
panic multiple times..

